1
00:01:05,856 --> 00:01:08,288
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,416 --> 00:01:11,328
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:15,296
(Fengyi Palace)

4
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,719
Good.

5
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,200
Bad.

6
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,040
Good.

7
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,640
Bad.

8
00:01:23,779 --> 00:01:24,440
Good.

9
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,600
Bad.

10
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,481
Beat her hard!

11
00:01:32,121 --> 00:01:34,800
Mother, I was wrong!

12
00:01:36,401 --> 00:01:39,041
Mother, I was wrong!

13
00:01:39,281 --> 00:01:40,960
Mother!

14
00:01:42,641 --> 00:01:43,761
I won't dare again!

15
00:01:43,761 --> 00:01:44,880
Mother!

16
00:01:50,841 --> 00:01:52,720
No way. I need to check.

17
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,320
What are you doing?

18
00:02:01,921 --> 00:02:04,080
With so many memorials piling up,

19
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,281
I wonder when you'd return.

20
00:02:05,681 --> 00:02:08,081
Are you worried about me?

21
00:02:08,401 --> 00:02:09,801
Who's worried about you?

22
00:02:10,561 --> 00:02:13,200
I'm afraid you'll anger Empress Dowager
and damage my body.

23
00:02:15,681 --> 00:02:16,561
Are you alright?

24
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,001
Jinming stepped in to mediate.

25
00:02:20,281 --> 00:02:21,401
How could Mother refuse?

26
00:02:23,521 --> 00:02:25,561
I told Mother,
to fulfill my filial duty,

27
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:29,200
His Majesty
personally taught me all night.

28
00:02:31,121 --> 00:02:32,801
Personally taught...

29
00:02:38,361 --> 00:02:39,521
All night...

30
00:02:57,121 --> 00:02:58,920
To fulfill filial duty...

31
00:03:00,841 --> 00:03:01,720
Your Majesty,

32
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,600
you've worked hard.

33
00:03:03,401 --> 00:03:04,361
Not at all.

34
00:03:05,961 --> 00:03:07,561
See how much the eyes resemble yours.

35
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,160
They also look like yours.

36
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,320
What are you thinking?

37
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,001
Don't talk nonsense.

38
00:03:17,001 --> 00:03:18,081
What filial duty?

39
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,121
I said,

40
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,160
His Majesty taught me
to play the zither all night,

41
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,081
so I could perform for Mother later

42
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,401
to fulfill my filial duty.

43
00:03:25,681 --> 00:03:27,081
Mother was deeply moved

44
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,281
and mentioned

45
00:03:28,401 --> 00:03:31,001
she wished the Empress could

46
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,081
learn embroidery.

47
00:03:33,281 --> 00:03:34,440
Embroidery?

48
00:03:34,681 --> 00:03:36,600
Mother knows well
I'm terrible at needlework.

49
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:38,961
Alright then.

50
00:03:40,841 --> 00:03:41,720
Let's switch.

51
00:03:49,681 --> 00:03:51,001
I choose embroidery then.

52
00:04:05,409 --> 00:04:05,920
Jinyun.

53
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:12,121
What new game are you two playing?

54
00:04:16,801 --> 00:04:19,601
Why are you here? Aren't you
with the Empress Dowager?

55
00:04:19,601 --> 00:04:20,921
I came to find my brother.

56
00:04:21,121 --> 00:04:22,440
Jinyun, pay me up.

57
00:04:24,121 --> 00:04:24,960
What is it about?

58
00:04:25,561 --> 00:04:26,721
Small matter.

59
00:04:26,801 --> 00:04:28,280
You promised to repay my debts.

60
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,280
Now I brought back your wife.

61
00:04:30,785 --> 00:04:31,320
Pay me up.

62
00:04:32,041 --> 00:04:32,561
How much?

63
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:34,840
8,000 taels.

64
00:04:35,561 --> 00:04:36,801
- 8,000 taels?
- 8,000 taels?

65
00:04:37,921 --> 00:04:38,880
In gold.

66
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,880
- In gold?
- In gold?

67
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,640
The bet with Third Uncle

68
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,121
is a complete scam.

69
00:04:44,121 --> 00:04:45,840
It was an archery contest against him.

70
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,640
He's a war veteran.

71
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,721
And I've only played cards.

72
00:04:47,721 --> 00:04:48,353
So...

73
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,840
Isn't it about archery?

74
00:04:55,721 --> 00:04:56,601
I'll win for you.

75
00:05:15,361 --> 00:05:17,080
Third Uncle,
what refined taste you have.

76
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,121
Your Majesty.

77
00:05:18,561 --> 00:05:19,232
Your Highness.

78
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,640
What brings you here to play with me?

79
00:05:22,241 --> 00:05:25,161
I heard you competed in archery
against Jinming recently

80
00:05:25,721 --> 00:05:27,241
and won 8,000 taels from him.

81
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,121
Do you dare compete against me today?

82
00:05:29,601 --> 00:05:30,640
If I win,

83
00:05:30,921 --> 00:05:32,361
the debt will be cleared.

84
00:05:32,361 --> 00:05:32,961
Right.

85
00:05:34,481 --> 00:05:35,440
Of course.

86
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:38,840
(Everyone in Chen Empire
knows the Emperor is bookish.)

87
00:05:39,617 --> 00:05:40,200
Jinyun.

88
00:05:40,601 --> 00:05:42,280
(Daring to challenge me in archery?)

89
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,001
Well shot!

90
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,361
Third Uncle.

91
00:06:19,801 --> 00:06:21,561
Now I owe you nothing.

92
00:06:22,121 --> 00:06:23,161
I admit defeat.

93
00:06:29,729 --> 00:06:30,320
Your Highness.

94
00:06:30,681 --> 00:06:33,440
Xiao Jinyun's constitution is frail.

95
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,880
Since when could he handle a bow?

96
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,601
Go investigate it.

97
00:06:49,801 --> 00:06:52,280
I never thought this pleasure house

98
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,121
would harbor such elegant melodies.

99
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,041
Jinming.

100
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:57,760
This place you brought me
is truly amazing.

101
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,481
Of course.

102
00:06:58,721 --> 00:06:59,400
Jinyun,

103
00:06:59,721 --> 00:07:01,241
we rarely get to come out like this.

104
00:07:01,241 --> 00:07:02,640
Going back early would be a waste.

105
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,241
Come on.

106
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:03,880
Let's drink.

107
00:07:04,609 --> 00:07:05,121
Let's drink.

108
00:07:18,081 --> 00:07:18,640
Good!

109
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,481
Well played!

110
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,801
May I ask you

111
00:07:27,801 --> 00:07:30,080
what the meaning
behind that piece I just played was?

112
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,320
Well...

113
00:07:32,681 --> 00:07:33,721
It's hard to tell.

114
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:37,241
Poetic sentiments grow cold
with few who understand.

115
00:07:37,561 --> 00:07:40,721
Yet I rejoice to meet you
by the riverside.

116
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:43,640
Only Mr. Xu truly comprehends music.

117
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,840
He understands me.

118
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,481
What?

119
00:07:47,921 --> 00:07:49,241
Mr. Xu?

120
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:53,824
(My elder brother isn't the one
to frequent such places.)

121
00:07:53,921 --> 00:07:54,801
(Could it be...)

122
00:07:55,041 --> 00:07:55,801
Exactly.

123
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:59,200
Before heading north,
Mr. Xu often gathered friends here.

124
00:07:59,361 --> 00:08:01,921
Many of his friends
were foreign dignitaries,

125
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,776
who only enjoyed drinking and revelry,

126
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,561
unlike Mr. Xu who comprehends music.

127
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,241
(Foreigners?)

128
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,481
(How dare she accuse
my family of treason!)

129
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,960
(I must inform His Majesty now.)

130
00:08:15,681 --> 00:08:16,760
Jinyun, are you leaving?

131
00:08:18,041 --> 00:08:19,320
Jinyun, wait for me!

132
00:08:23,361 --> 00:08:24,320
Everyone, leave.

133
00:08:33,441 --> 00:08:34,601
Inform our master

134
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:37,241
that His Majesty has grown
suspicious of the Xu family.

135
00:08:37,481 --> 00:08:38,001
Yes.

136
00:08:41,481 --> 00:08:42,040
Your Majesty.

137
00:08:42,241 --> 00:08:42,760
Your Majesty.

138
00:08:43,081 --> 00:08:43,961
Listen to me.

139
00:08:51,481 --> 00:08:52,001
Your Majesty.

140
00:08:52,361 --> 00:08:53,081
What's wrong?

141
00:08:53,241 --> 00:08:54,040
Are you okay?

142
00:08:58,817 --> 00:08:59,400
Your Majesty.

143
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,361
Are you having your period?

144
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:04,201
I am the Emperor!

145
00:09:04,481 --> 00:09:06,201
How could I have a period?

146
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,160
Your Majesty,

147
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,800
your current body is that of a woman.

148
00:09:16,121 --> 00:09:17,001
As a woman,

149
00:09:17,201 --> 00:09:18,400
you'll naturally have periods.

150
00:09:19,001 --> 00:09:21,841
During your period,
you'll need to use a sanitary cloth.

151
00:09:22,481 --> 00:09:24,400
Relax, everyone struggles initially.

152
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:24,961
I'll show you.

153
00:09:24,961 --> 00:09:25,481
Wait.

154
00:09:26,481 --> 00:09:28,400
Do not use my body for such acts.

155
00:09:29,241 --> 00:09:30,081
Come on.

156
00:09:31,585 --> 00:09:32,160
Your Majesty.

157
00:09:40,081 --> 00:09:41,601
This water is poisonous.

158
00:09:42,001 --> 00:09:42,601
Your Majesty,

159
00:09:42,961 --> 00:09:44,721
you can't handle cold water, right?

160
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:46,121
I have a cold constitution.

161
00:09:46,481 --> 00:09:48,040
When I first had my period at fourteen,

162
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:51,040
I've endured pain every month since.

163
00:09:51,441 --> 00:09:52,800
Hot foods cause irritation.

164
00:09:53,081 --> 00:09:54,321
Cold foods bring stomachache.

165
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,520
How did you endure this?

166
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:57,760
Just let it be

167
00:09:57,961 --> 00:09:58,920
and get used to it.

168
00:10:00,001 --> 00:10:02,760
I've told Xuan to prepare
ginger and jujube tea for you.

169
00:10:05,121 --> 00:10:06,481
But I thought you disliked ginger.

170
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,081
I personally brought you ice cream,

171
00:10:16,081 --> 00:10:17,081
yet you dismissed it.

172
00:10:17,361 --> 00:10:20,081
It seems you truly don't care for me.

173
00:10:20,081 --> 00:10:23,481
I said I'll only have ginger
and jujube tea today.

174
00:10:24,081 --> 00:10:26,201
Since Consort Zhao and others
have had this ice cream,

175
00:10:27,321 --> 00:10:28,760
I don't need to taste them then.

176
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,560
I've known you since childhood.

177
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,800
How could I not know you dislike ginger?

178
00:10:34,721 --> 00:10:36,841
There are many things
you don't know about me.

179
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,560
What I once disliked,

180
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,201
I now appreciate.

181
00:10:41,841 --> 00:10:43,241
What I once cherished,

182
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,441
I don't quite like it.

183
00:10:46,841 --> 00:10:48,361
It seems I'm not welcome

184
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,841
at your Fengyi Palace.

185
00:10:51,841 --> 00:10:52,640
Prepare to leave!

186
00:10:52,961 --> 00:10:54,400
Go to Consort Zhao's quarters.

187
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,640
Ginger tea dispels cold.

188
00:11:05,321 --> 00:11:06,481
It makes you feel better.

189
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,321
Here.

190
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:32,800
Rest assured.

191
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,721
The pain will subside soon
after drinking it.

192
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:43,961
Let's go.

193
00:11:44,721 --> 00:11:45,841
I'll help you rest.

194
00:11:50,689 --> 00:11:51,321
Your Majesty.

195
00:11:52,001 --> 00:11:52,560
I'm okay.

196
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,800
Let me carry you.

197
00:11:54,201 --> 00:11:54,920
No need.

198
00:12:17,241 --> 00:12:19,880
(Just once has left me
in excruciating pain.)

199
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:22,680
(Xu Yu endures this every single month,)

200
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:25,321
(but I was never by her side.)

201
00:12:35,081 --> 00:12:35,680
Alright.

202
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,560
This way you won't feel cold.

203
00:12:38,441 --> 00:12:39,640
I'll sleep in the outer room.

204
00:12:39,841 --> 00:12:41,121
Call me if you need help.

205
00:12:44,129 --> 00:12:46,680
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

206
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,280
The outer room gets cold at night.

207
00:12:48,601 --> 00:12:49,961
Just sleep here.

208
00:12:50,081 --> 00:12:52,880
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

209
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,601
Fine.

210
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,128
It's your first time having period.

211
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,081
Then, I could care for you.

212
00:12:59,265 --> 00:13:01,793
♪Console my grieving soul♪

213
00:13:02,081 --> 00:13:06,721
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

214
00:13:07,233 --> 00:13:08,737
♪If not for letting go♪

215
00:13:08,993 --> 00:13:12,201
♪How could I bear to shatter this dream♪

216
00:13:12,201 --> 00:13:13,160
- Turn around.
- Turn around.

217
00:13:13,601 --> 00:13:19,190
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

218
00:13:19,841 --> 00:13:23,233
♪Like her, like me, like you.
Hairpins carved♪

219
00:13:23,483 --> 00:13:24,920
♪With endless sighs and regrets♪

220
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,920
Xu Yu.

221
00:13:26,753 --> 00:13:29,081
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

222
00:13:29,081 --> 00:13:31,920
You've been busy
taking care of me all day.

223
00:13:32,241 --> 00:13:33,961
Do you care about me?

224
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:36,201
Who'd care about you?

225
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,760
I'm caring for my own body.

226
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,560
If this causes lasting health problems,

227
00:13:41,241 --> 00:13:42,601
you can't do anything about it.

228
00:13:44,065 --> 00:13:46,145
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

229
00:13:46,753 --> 00:13:48,321
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

230
00:13:48,321 --> 00:13:49,081
Xu Yu.

231
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:53,760
Just say the word,
and I'll make it happen for you.

232
00:13:53,825 --> 00:13:55,623
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

233
00:13:57,160 --> 00:14:00,001
Things you couldn't do before,
you can do now?

234
00:14:00,721 --> 00:14:01,411
When have I...

235
00:14:01,411 --> 00:14:02,321
Enough, Your Majesty.

236
00:14:03,601 --> 00:14:04,280
Rest now.

237
00:14:04,321 --> 00:14:07,681
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

238
00:14:09,313 --> 00:14:13,400
♪The same joys and sorrows
can't be relived♪

239
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,280
(Xiao Jinyun.)

240
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:17,040
(You promised me so many things before,)

241
00:14:17,721 --> 00:14:19,361
(but I'm sure
you've forgotten them all.)

242
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:21,280
(Never mind.)

243
00:14:21,721 --> 00:14:23,040
(I'm used to it anyway.)

244
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:24,880
(With no expectations,)

245
00:14:25,241 --> 00:14:26,400
(perhaps it's better.)

246
00:14:38,817 --> 00:14:41,633
(Four years ago)

247
00:14:48,721 --> 00:14:49,680
Your Highness.

248
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,081
Why are you here?

249
00:14:53,361 --> 00:14:54,841
Today is your birthday banquet.

250
00:14:54,841 --> 00:14:56,481
Why are you alone out here?

251
00:14:56,513 --> 00:14:58,441
♪Loving to walk behind you♪

252
00:14:58,441 --> 00:14:59,721
Many come to congratulate me,

253
00:15:00,441 --> 00:15:03,040
but none are sincere.

254
00:15:03,041 --> 00:15:04,280
♪Even the night breeze turns gentle♪

255
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,841
I'd rather watch the snow here.

256
00:15:07,721 --> 00:15:10,560
Snow silently nourishes all things.

257
00:15:10,625 --> 00:15:13,721
♪Those drops of happiness I feel♪

258
00:15:13,721 --> 00:15:15,481
Why are you sneaking out of the banquet?

259
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,321
Even without your robe.

260
00:15:17,321 --> 00:15:19,481
♪Time seemed to freeze♪

261
00:15:19,481 --> 00:15:21,001
You are also dressed just as lightly.

262
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:27,321
Thank you, Your Highness.

263
00:15:27,329 --> 00:15:29,361
♪How I wish to hold your hand tightly♪

264
00:15:29,361 --> 00:15:30,201
Your Highness.

265
00:15:31,241 --> 00:15:32,841
Did you make a wish?

266
00:15:32,841 --> 00:15:34,201
♪Walking with you to the road's end♪

267
00:15:34,201 --> 00:15:35,601
I've never believed in such things.

268
00:15:35,961 --> 00:15:38,760
We have to fight for
whatever we want by ourselves.

269
00:15:39,321 --> 00:15:40,601
How can we leave it to fate?

270
00:15:40,641 --> 00:15:44,441
♪Yet I can't escape fate's tricks♪

271
00:15:44,441 --> 00:15:46,121
You're being too serious.

272
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,121
Just making a wish.

273
00:15:48,321 --> 00:15:50,001
It's just a small ritual.

274
00:15:50,001 --> 00:15:51,040
Think about it.

275
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:53,201
If this wish actually comes true,

276
00:15:53,201 --> 00:15:54,800
that would be so wonderful.

277
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,486
♪Can we stay silent♪

278
00:15:56,486 --> 00:15:57,441
♪Watching the scenery slowly change♪

279
00:15:57,441 --> 00:15:59,241
If it doesn't come true,

280
00:15:59,241 --> 00:16:01,280
then we'd strive toward that goal.

281
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:03,441
So what wish did you make?

282
00:16:03,553 --> 00:16:05,400
♪Words have failed me♪

283
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:06,520
I...

284
00:16:08,481 --> 00:16:10,481
I wish for peace in Chen.

285
00:16:11,241 --> 00:16:13,481
And I wish you and me

286
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:16,601
will both be happy,

287
00:16:16,961 --> 00:16:18,081
and be ourselves

288
00:16:18,361 --> 00:16:20,321
at any time.

289
00:16:27,481 --> 00:16:28,040
Very well.

290
00:16:28,601 --> 00:16:30,081
I'll make a wish too.

291
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,520
I wish that from now on,

292
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:35,280
I could remember every wish Xu Yu makes,

293
00:16:36,321 --> 00:16:37,640
year after year.

294
00:17:07,489 --> 00:17:12,673
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

295
00:17:13,409 --> 00:17:17,972
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

296
00:17:19,297 --> 00:17:24,712
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

297
00:17:25,281 --> 00:17:29,825
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

298
00:17:30,465 --> 00:17:35,729
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

299
00:17:36,097 --> 00:17:41,774
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

300
00:17:42,113 --> 00:17:44,129
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

301
00:17:44,321 --> 00:17:48,065
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

302
00:17:48,641 --> 00:17:53,313
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

303
00:17:53,857 --> 00:17:55,617
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

304
00:17:55,937 --> 00:17:59,553
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

305
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:05,327
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
